name: The Dream of the Drowning Kid
description:
Below the surface of a deep lake, 
There is a kid, died long ago
No one was ever close to know his name,
Drowning was his hero

Under the water, there is always silence,
Lots of time for dreaming 
He can not believe,
His salvation was dying

He dreams what he needs, 
He may have died years ago,
But here,
He is living in the dreams
